{"word":"δάπεδον","slug":"δάπεδον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>δάπεδον</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>prob. for <el>ζάπεδον</el>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> <el>διάπεδον.</el>\n<p/><i>any level surface: the floor of a chamber</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; also, <el>γῆς δάπεδον</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; and <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>the ground</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>: <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <i>plains</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/>"}]}